Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:32.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}You go, I go! We go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:34.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Dream on!!
